data.description: Best and final offers by 3pm Wednesday 4/17. Welcome to the desirable Oak Ridge neighborhood! This 3 bed, 1.5 bath home has been tastefully designed to offer you ample space to entertain, or relax by the cozy fire after a long day. The newly installed outdoor space provides the perfect backdrop for hosting a summer bbq. Or if catching the game in the heated/cooled bar room is more your speed, this home has it all! The 2 zone AC system, vinyl fence and patio are two years old. Gleaming hardwood floors throughout the home add easy maintenance and style. Only a few short miles from the beautiful beaches, easy access to the parkway, or a short commute to JBMDL. Come make this house your home and enjoy all it has to offer, just in time for summer!
